Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <substparams> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT substparams (expression?, substparam*)>
 <!ATTLIST substparams
      condition           CDATA     IMPLIED
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
